AnalyticsAgent

CodeAgent

ResearchAgent



---

3. 🌐 Domain Routing Layer

Routes requests into isolated pipelines:

🏥 medical pipeline (HIPAA-safe)

🎮 gaming pipeline

💰 financial pipeline

📱 social media pipeline

🔬 research pipeline


Each pipeline = separate rules + models + storage


---

4. 🔐 Policy & Safety Engine (IMPORTANT)

role-based access control (RBAC)

data classification (public / private / sensitive)

action permissions

audit requirements


👉 This prevents misuse and keeps system enterprise-safe.


---

5. 📊 Data Layer

PostgreSQL (structured data)

Redis (fast cache)

Vector DB (FAISS / Weaviate)

Object storage (S3-compatible)

Optional: IPFS for immutable logs



---

6. 📡 Event Bus (REAL-TIME backbone)

Kafka / NATS / RabbitMQ


Used for:

telemetry

logs

agent communication

workflow triggers



---

7. 🧾 Audit & Transparency Layer

NOT blockchain-first — use blockchain only optionally.

Core:

append-only logs

hash verification

trace IDs per request


Optional:

Ethereum / Hyperledger anchoring



